<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to AWARI</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5aa0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .welcome-title {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2c5aa0;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #1e3d6f;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .feature-item::before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">AWARI</div>
            <h1 class="welcome-title">Welcome to AWARI!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= user.firstName %></strong>,</p>
            
            <p>Welcome to AWARI! We're thrilled to have you join our community of property owners, agents, and guests.</p>
            
            <p>AWARI is your one-stop platform for:</p>
            
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-item">Finding and booking amazing short-term rentals</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Listing your properties for rent or sale</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Connecting with verified property owners and agents</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Secure payment processing</div>
                <div class="feature-item">24/7 customer support</div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Ready to get started? Click the button below to explore our platform and discover amazing properties.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= actionUrl || 'https://awari.com/dashboard' %>" class="cta-button">
                    <%= actionText || 'Get Started' %>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Happy exploring!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The AWARI Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent to <%= user.email %>. If you didn't create an account with AWARI, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 AWARI. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

